Perl-Critic-Policy-Local-RequireArgUnpackOrShift version 0.01
=======================================================

This Perl::Critic policy is intended to address the OO Perl idiom of using
something like "my $self = shift;" before assigning @_ to an arg hash.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Perl::Critic

